[No. 5,899. In Bank.] BOARD OF EDUCATION v. WHEELER MARTIN ET AL. Evidence. Appeal from a judgment for defendants, in the Nineteenth District Court, City and County of San Francisco. Wheeler, J.

John J. Williams, and W. C. Burnett, for Appellant.

Bishop & Fifield, for Respondents.

The Court:

On the authority of the Board of Education v. Keenan, 55 Cal. 642, judgment and order of nonsuit reversed, and cause remanded for a new trial.

*140McKinstry, J., dissented.

[Thornton, J., being disqualified,, took no part in the decision.]
